      "content": "but that's the thing, tiny steps don't work anymore. i've taken all the steps. i've done the therapy, the habits, the \"one day at a time\" stuff. it doesn't matter. the loop just keeps resetting. it feels like no matter how much i move, i'm just standing in the same place. it's just... endless. i can't see a version of the future that isn't just more of this same cycle.",
